{"tha-ap55:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap55:0.2":"Bijanivagga ","tha-ap55:0.3":"Sayanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap55:1.1":"“Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap55:1.2":"sabbalokanukampino; ","tha-ap55:1.3":"Sayanam tassa padasim, ","tha-ap55:1.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap55:2.1":"Tena sayanadanena, ","tha-ap55:2.2":"sukhette bijasampada; ","tha-ap55:2.3":"Bhoga nibbattare tassa, ","tha-ap55:2.4":"sayanassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap55:3.1":"Akase seyyam kappemi, ","tha-ap55:3.2":"dharemi pathavim imam; ","tha-ap55:3.3":"Panesu me issariyam, ","tha-ap55:3.4":"sayanassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap55:4.1":"Pancakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap55:4.2":"attha asum mahateja; ","tha-ap55:4.3":"Catuttimse kappasate, ","tha-ap55:4.4":"caturo ca mahabbala. ","tha-ap55:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap55:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap55:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap55:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sayanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap55:7.1":"Sayanadayakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}